videos.headline: Iowa runs play-action to perfection for TD
videos.description: Iowa quarterback C. J. Beathard bootlegs out after the play-action and finds George Kittle wide open for the 10-yard touchdown to take a 7-0 lead.

videos.headline: Iowa's Hesse with the easy pick-six
videos.description: Iowa's Parker Hesse gets in the way of the Nebraska swing pass making the interception and waltzing into the end zone from four yards out to give the Hawkeyes a 14-7 lead.

videos.headline: Canzeri goes untouched for Iowa TD
videos.description: Iowa's Jordan Canzeri takes the handoff to the left and goes 29 yards untouched into the end zone, giving the Hawkeyes a two score lead.

videos.headline: Canzeri puts on the jets, goes 67 yards for TD
videos.description: Iowa's Jordan Canzeri finds a hole and goes 67 yards untouched for his second touchdown of the game to put the Hawkeyes up 28-17.

videos.headline: Reilly makes ridiculous catch between his legs
videos.description: Nebraska's Brandon Reilly can't make the initial catch when falling over, but he regains possession of it between his legs for the 27-yard gain.
